text: Against All Odds (2009) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view event made by Total Nonstop Action Wrestling (TNA). It took place on February 8, 2009 at the Impact! Zone in Orlando, Florida. It was the fifth Against All Odds event held by TNA and their first PPV event to air in High-Definition. == Results == == References == == Other websites == * Against All Odds at In Demand.com * The Official website of Against All Odds * TNA Wrestling.com Category:2009 in professional wrestling Category:Sports in Orlando, Florida Category:2009 in American television Category:2000s in Orlando, Florida Category:2009 in Florida Category:February 2009 events
